"body":"要是遇到了這種狀況，我也想和巴跟燐子學姊一樣\n好好地表現出真實的自己，\n然後去尊敬自己親眼看到的對方","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev171-me4-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"嗯嗯，我覺得這種想法很棒","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev171-me4-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"啊！　抱歉，麻里奈小姐\n你明明是來買麵包的，我卻一直自顧自地說","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev171-me4-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"麻里奈","body":"不會哦，倒不如說能聽小綾分享，我也很開心。\n如果之後還有拍到好照片，記得要再找我聊聊喔","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev171-me4-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"好的，到時候我會再聯絡你，請一定要來找我","tention":